what_worked: Applied union_cte_split, single_pass_aggregation, prefetch_fact_join: Split UNION into separate per-channel CTEs with pre-filtered dimension tables (date_dim, item) and early year filtering, then union aggregated results.
why_it_worked: Splitting complex UNION into separate CTEs enables per-branch optimization; Consolidating repeated scans into CASE aggregates reduces I/O from N scans to 1; Pre-joining filtered dimensions with fact table before aggregation reduces join input
